code: @Override public XContentBuilder toXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.startObject().     if (from != null) {         builder.field(FROM.getPreferredName(), from).     }     if (size != null) {         builder.field(SIZE.getPreferredName(), size).     }     builder.endObject().     return builder. }
@Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(from, size). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (obj == null) {         return false.     }     if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     }     PageParams other = (PageParams) obj.     return Objects.equals(from, other.from) && Objects.equals(size, other.size). }
